p: The samples from the 96 well plate that showed bioactivity were linked to the LC-ESI-QTOF-MS/MS chromatogram by time. The active compounds with MS and MS/MS data were tentatively identified: the mass data were compared with previous reports and using public databases ((the Human Metabolomics Database; http://www.hmdb.ca; accessed on 30 December 2019), Chemspider ( http://www.chemspider.com; accessed on 30 December 2019), and Metlin database ( https://metlin.scripps.edu; accessed on 30 December 2019)).
